exerciseStep: 1. Slide your chair closer to the wall if needed.
2. Look towards the ceiling, there should be a little circle on the right side in front of you.
3. Look below the circle, there should be a square.
4. Look below the square, there should be a triangle.
5. With your right hand, place your hand on the white circle on the wall.
6. Move your hand from the circle
7. Reach towards the square with your right hand.
8. Reach towards the triangle with your right hand, go as far as you can comfortably go.
9. Slowly glide your hand down the wall.
10. Repeat steps 5 to 9, with placing your right hand on the circle
11. Then move your hand from the circle
12. Reach towards the square with your right hand
13. Then reach overhead to the triangle with your right hand
14. Finish by slowly bringing your hand down to each shape again.
